Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.34,0:00:16.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在圣所看到马吉了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I saw Makee on Sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.01,0:00:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－马吉死了－我知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Makee's dead. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我亲手杀的她\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I shot her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.18,0:00:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你对圣所事件的描述\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Your account of events on Sanctuary
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人怀疑\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}has proven dubious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.15,0:00:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你们这帮混蛋怎么想的 我曾经也是你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I know how you assholes think. I was you once.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.06,0:00:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他事可以做 其他的方式活下去\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There's other things to be, other ways to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.03,0:00:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不许放弃\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't you quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.06,0:00:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道凯瑟琳·哈尔西在哪\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I know the location of Catherine Halsey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说不是钱的问题 对不对\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's not about the money for you, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.17,0:00:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是她对你做了什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's about what she did to ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.47,0:00:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,索伦绝不会丢下你们任何一个人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Soren never would've left any of you behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你被捕了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You're under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁比·安买下了索伦的船员\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Ruby Ann bought Soren's crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.84,0:00:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我爸回来 他就会保护我们\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}When my dad comes back, he'll protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.68,0:00:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他回不来了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}He's not coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.71,0:00:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想给你介绍个人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I want to introduce you to someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这位是朱莉娅 她将是你的随从\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This is Julia. She'll be your attendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.25,0:00:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在哪儿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:01:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,科塔娜  她很安全\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Cortana, she's secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.32,0:01:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给你的问题有什么进展吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Have you made any progress with the problem I gave you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.76,0:01:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管采取什么行动\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}All of my simulations returned the same result,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我所有模拟结果都是一样的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}regardless of any action taken.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以没什么可做的了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}So there's nothing to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当时在扫描波段\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I was scanning the band,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.74,0:01:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后就听到了干扰中有声音\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and I heard something in the interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.57,0:01:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你听到了一段信息\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You heard a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.91,0:01:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况还会再次发生\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This will happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:21.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你去寻找\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I want you to post your evidence
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.28,0:01:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星盟其他活动的证据\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}of the Covenant's other activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.08,0:01:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,按下按钮 我就会来找你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Press the button, and I'll find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.35,0:01:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新来的这人 让我们护送一个技术团队\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This new guy, he's got us escorting a tech team
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,执行什么修复任务\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}on some fix-it mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.12,0:01:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你要派钴队去另个通讯中继站\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}If you're sending Cobalt to another comms array,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.72,0:01:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好告诉他们可能会碰到星盟\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}you better tell them to expect the Covenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.89,0:01:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会授权银队\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I cannot authorize Silver Team
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.92,0:01:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,执行战斗任务\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}to perform combat operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我们可以作战了吗－是的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- We're cleared for combat? - Affirmative.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.07,0:01:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任务具体内容是什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What exactly is the mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.61,0:01:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在致远星的星盟\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The Covenant's on Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有七公里到达目的地\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Seven clicks to target.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里兹\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Riz?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.13,0:02:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钴队三号 R队 这里是银队三号结束\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Cobalt Three, Romeo, this is Silver Three, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.34,0:02:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钴队队员 这里是银队三号\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Any Cobalt element, this is Silver Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:27.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们正前往你处 收到了吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We are en route to your position, how copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.91,0:02:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试下中继站\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Try the relay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韦谢格勒中继站 这里是银队三号\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Visegrád Relay, this is Silver Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,检查无线信号 完毕\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Radio check, over.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.29,0:02:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有空中支援吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We getting air support for this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.02,0:02:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,韦谢格勒中继站 这里是银队三号\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Visegrád Relay, this is Silver Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.66,0:02:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where is everybody?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.92,0:02:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－完毕－就我们自己\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Over. - We're on our own.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.43,0:02:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰队指挥部不相信致远星上有星盟\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}FLEETCOM doesn't believe the Covenant's on Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.96,0:02:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们只认为钴队不见了而已\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They just think Cobalt's missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.47,0:02:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次是搜救任务\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This is a search and rescue mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们要考虑到钴队可能\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}but we need to be prepared for the possibility
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到什么东西了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}that Cobalt ran into something.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星盟吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Something Covenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:02:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指挥部认为这个星球对方过不来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Command thinks this planet's untouchable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们没看到我们所看到的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They haven't seen what we've seen,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.78,0:03:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不如我们了解情况\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and they don't know what we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这么说吧 我们会不可避免地遇上他们\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'll tell you this, we will have contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那之前 就只有我们\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Until then, it's just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.79,0:03:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得这样合适吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This seem right to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看能不能恢复电力\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}See if you can get the power up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,收到 士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Copy, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走的时候很匆忙\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Left in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.54,0:05:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有钴队踪迹 也没有破坏的痕迹\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No sign of Cobalt, no breach marks at the--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚什么动静\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What the hell was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.73,0:06:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚 从没听过\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't know, I've never heard anything like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.83,0:06:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听过 在圣所听见的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I have, on Sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.81,0:06:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在信他了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You believe him now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退下\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Stand down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.40,0:07:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你队员把武器放下 士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell your team to lower their weapons, Master Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.14,0:07:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这什么意思\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.94,0:07:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-士官长  -立刻\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Chief? - Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都描述不出来你们处境有多糟糕\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I can't even describe the amount of shit you're in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.31,0:07:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都描述不出来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I can't even describe
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.75,0:07:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的脸会发生什么事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}what's about to happen to your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.25,0:07:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这帮人谁啊\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Who the hell are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有舰队指挥部的头号命令\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I carry priority orders from FLEETCOM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－什么命令－将你们带回\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- What orders? - To bring you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.82,0:07:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你妨碍了我的任务 让开\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You are impeding my mission, move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.72,0:07:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有任务\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There is no mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－你偷了一架兀鹰－什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- You stole a Condor. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－伪造飞行计划－她说什么呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Falsified a flight plan. - What is she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在都不允许穿战斗装备\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You're not even authorized to be in those suits right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更别提拿枪指着我的脸了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}let alone pointing a gun at my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.27,0:07:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以退下 否则我们就动手了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}So stand down, or we will engage you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那祝你们好运\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Good luck with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士官长 我们该怎么办\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Chief, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:08:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钴队呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where is Cobalt Team?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.11,0:08:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－最后机会－约翰\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Last chance. - John.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我钴队在哪 要不然我就进去了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell me where Cobalt is, or I'm going through that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是来给你下命令的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I gave you an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What's the call?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.32,0:08:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退下 不许开火\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Ah, stand down, do not fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－士官长－他们来过\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Chief. - They were here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以证明\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I can prove it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.97,0:08:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样证明的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Not like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在一千英尺高的地方\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We were a thousand feet up,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.88,0:08:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风在呼啸 电缆嘎吱作响\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}wind whipping, cables groaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里的温度不超过2度\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Couldn't have been more than two degrees up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.66,0:08:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 一月 懂的吧  －嗯\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- January, you know? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我撑不住了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And I can't hold it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.13,0:08:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被绑在安全带上 往下看\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm strapped in the harness, and I look down,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.13,0:08:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉亚瑟 说"我得释放一下"\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I tell Arthur, I say, "I gotta go."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.57,0:09:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他该怎么办\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What's he gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你尿在亚瑟叔叔身上了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You peed on Uncle Arthur?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尿他身上了 他能怎么办\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I peed on him. What could he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 抬下巴\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Okay, lift your chin up, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What the hell's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这故事很好笑呀\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This shit is funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可我以前听过\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, I've heard it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.35,0:09:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那又有什么区别\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What difference does that make?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.19,0:09:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我重复讲的时候你就应该笑\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You're supposed to damn well laugh when I repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.73,0:09:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老糊涂的人是我\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm the one that's senile.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都不知道你在抱怨什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't know what you're complaining about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没在抱怨\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm not complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.20,0:09:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想抱怨来着\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, I mean, you want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.27,0:09:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会替你保密的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Your secret's safe with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.17,0:09:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是跟那件\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Is this about that thing
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.71,0:09:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不该告诉我的事有关吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}that you weren't supposed to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不该记得的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You weren't supposed to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记得什么又不是我能选的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't choose what I forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.62,0:09:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可能得走了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I might have to go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.09,0:09:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪儿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.69,0:09:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没法带你一起走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And I can't take you with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我知道－我想带的可是没法带\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- I know. - I want to, but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到那座桥了吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You see that bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我阻止不了 爸\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I can't stop it, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那座桥是谁建的不\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You know who built that bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.78,0:10:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我说了算的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's not up to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:18.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 太迟了－我建的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- It's too late. - I built that bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你亚瑟叔叔\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Me and your Uncle Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竣工那天\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The day it was finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和你妈 你姐姐一起踏上了那座桥\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I walked across it with your mum, and your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.26,0:10:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她那会儿还不到13岁\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She couldn't have been more than three.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牵着她的小手\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Held her little hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不让我抱\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She wouldn't let me pick her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.07,0:10:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想一路走完全程\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She wanted to walk the whole way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.84,0:10:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.94,0:10:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她什么时候来啊\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}So when's she coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.18,0:10:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你姐\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.65,0:10:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她走了 爸\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She's gone, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:11:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱莉娅走了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Julia's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈也是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Mum, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.53,0:11:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 就剩你跟我了－我知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- It's just you and me. - I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.10,0:11:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当然知道了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I damn well know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别以为我不知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't think that I don't know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.18,0:11:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我只是 对不起 有时候我脑子会糊涂\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Sorry, I just, sorry, I just get confused sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.22,0:11:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.32,0:11:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不代表我不知道什么是真实的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Doesn't mean that I don't know what's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天见  好吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}See you tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.67,0:11:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 保证   －我保证\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Promise me... - Yeah, I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.41,0:11:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 答应我别让他们把我活捉\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No, promise me you won't let them take me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擅离职守\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Absent without leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.85,0:12:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,未经授权使用武器系统\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}unauthorized deployment of weapons systems,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.76,0:12:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,违反\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}violation of,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.52,0:12:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们管偷一架该死的兀鹰叫什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I mean, what do you even call stealing a goddamn Condor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:16.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这违反了15项《军队统一法典》的规定\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm looking at 15 infractions of the UCMJ,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其中一项涉及将上膛的武器\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}one of which involves pointing a loaded weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,指着军官的脸\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}in the face of an officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我干的 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I did that, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.94,0:12:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,长官 我有可靠消息\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Sir, I had credible information.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你那是感觉 是妄想\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You had a feeling. You had a delusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:29.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你越界了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You went outside the chain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.38,0:12:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不对\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Didn't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.02,0:12:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立即生效\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Effective immediately,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.59,0:12:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,银队暂停作战\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Silver Team is suspended from combat operations,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.86,0:12:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直到另行通知\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}'til further notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯斯上将 我知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Admiral Keyes, I know--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道个屁 因为你就不该知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You know nothing because it's not your job to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.80,0:12:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我的事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.04,0:12:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作就是服从命令\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Your job is to follow orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.57,0:12:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钴队到过韦谢格勒 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Cobalt was at Visegrád, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.88,0:13:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四天前 钴队被派往阿克蒂斯四号\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Four days ago, Cobalt was deployed to Aktis IV.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No, this isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.96,0:13:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看过钴队飞行计划\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I saw Cobalt's flight plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－士官长－我看到了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Chief. - I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.96,0:13:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们给篡改了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They changed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.80,0:13:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我清楚自己看到了什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I know what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.44,0:13:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰-117被解除现役\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}John-117 is relieved from active duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在通过精神评估之前\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and will be confined to barracks
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.45,0:13:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得离开营房\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}'til such a time as he clears a psychiatric evaluation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,117将接受精神化学检查\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}117 will submit to neurochemical--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你的命令 还是阿克森的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Is this you, or is this Ackerson?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.79,0:13:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰 别说了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}John, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整理服装 解散\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Rack your suits, dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.30,0:13:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有试过为我们辩护吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Did you even try to defend us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.67,0:14:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是你不用面对军事法庭审判的唯一原因\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm the only reason you're not facing a court-martial.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你骗我们\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You lied to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把完成任务需要知道的事都告诉你们了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I told you what you needed to know to complete the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－根本没有任务－钴队就在韦谢格勒\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- There was no mission. - Cobalt was at Visegrád.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－士官长 能谈谈吗－是海军情报局干的 这一切\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Chief, can I talk to you? - This is ONI, all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－是阿克森干的－不是吧 士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- This is Ackerson. - Come on, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－不然他干嘛来这－听不下去了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Why do you think he's here? - I can't listen to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.39,0:14:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们要去哪儿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瓦纳克\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Vannak!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－你失控了－什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- You are out of control. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你脑子不清楚 反复无常\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You're not thinking straight, you're erratic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.73,0:14:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候也开始质疑我的判断了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Since when do you question my judgment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.50,0:14:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从你开始看见死人开始\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Since you started seeing dead people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.20,0:14:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在圣所看见马吉这事我谁都没告诉\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I didn't tell anyone you said you saw Makee on Sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.21,0:14:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰 我想帮你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}John, I'm trying to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.04,0:14:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想以朋友身份跟你谈谈\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm trying to talk to you, as your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.55,0:14:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我用不着朋友 下士 我要的是斯巴达战士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't need a friend, Petty Officer, I need a Spartan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.72,0:14:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不试着当个称职的战士呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Why don't you try doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,125 你不能解散\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}125, you are not dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.74,0:15:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.06,0:15:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是谁啊\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-关  -嘘\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Kwan? - Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.54,0:15:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.95,0:15:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－你有危险－我看得出来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- You're in danger. - I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.88,0:15:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不   是鲁比·安要动你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Not from Ruby Ann.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是说你们的船员\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm talking about your crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.99,0:15:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁比·安把他们买通了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Ruby Ann bought them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.06,0:16:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－他们摆脱了索伦－什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- They got rid of Soren. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－接下来就是你－什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- You're next. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.43,0:16:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,索伦是不是－我不知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Is Soren-- - I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.06,0:16:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你赶紧带上凯斯勒走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You have to get Kessler and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－拜托 我干掉你了哎－才没有\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Come on, man, I got you. - Did not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑吗 这个距离\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Are you kidding me, at this range?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.61,0:16:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 拜托 兄弟－这是士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Come on, man. - It's Master Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  是士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah, it's Master Chief,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.52,0:16:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大卸八块了嘛\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}in eight different pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 你打偏了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Nope, nope, you missed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:34.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.29,0:16:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们干嘛呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩呀\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有好消息\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We have good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.33,0:16:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞船修好了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Ship's fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以出发了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We can leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.27,0:16:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你之前说要几天时间的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You said it would take a couple of days.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.64,0:16:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那可是索伦\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's Soren.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我们加班干了整宿  －过来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- We worked all night. - Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－没玩儿完呢   －凯斯勒\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- We're not finished. - Kessler.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该走了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Time to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.79,0:17:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能去吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Can I come?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.99,0:17:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－好呀  －不行\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Yeah. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.52,0:17:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有人都去\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Everybody goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,0:17:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们是一家人嘛\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We're all family.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.66,0:17:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们先过去 我一会儿去飞船跟你们汇合\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You go ahead, I'll meet you at the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.33,0:17:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们可以等\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We can wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.83,0:17:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必麻烦 我能行的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't trouble yourselves, I can manage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－卡丽娜  －不麻烦\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Carina. - It's no trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:27.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡丽娜\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Carina.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.18,0:17:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去拿你东西\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Get your things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.68,0:18:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关 你可以出来了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Kwan, you can come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.10,0:18:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们当初加入海军情报局的时候 就想干这事吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}So, when you guys joined ONI, is this what you had in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也不喜欢这样 士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We don't like this any more than you do, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们再靠近点\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}If you get any closer,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.45,0:18:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就得谈谈此刻的感觉了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}we're gonna have to talk about our feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.11,0:18:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是例行的心理评估 士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's just a routine psych eval, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.96,0:18:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－抱歉－什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Sorry. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－嗨－嘿 里兹\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Hi. - Hey, Riz.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.48,0:19:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们把我们的训练取消了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They canceled our training.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我干坐在铺位上 然后就\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I was sitting in my bunk, so--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就决定过来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}So you decided to come by here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.46,0:19:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.30,0:19:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看我发现谁了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Look who I found.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 一起吃晚饭呀\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hey, join us for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.77,0:19:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约会之夜泡汤了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There goes date night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.17,0:19:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.60,0:19:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会不会 别听他的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No, no, no, no, don't listen to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他对约会之夜的想法就是他听着\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}His idea of date night ends with him falling asleep
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.34,0:19:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卫星信号入睡 而我则去洗碗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}listening to the sat-link, and me doing the dishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,宝儿 不是你洗碗 是机器洗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Babe, you don't do the dishes, the machine does.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总得有人按按钮吧 过来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Someone has to press the button, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.32,0:19:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你饿了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You know, I hope you're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃完饭我给你治疗一下吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I can give you some treatment after we eat, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来不是治疗的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, I didn't really come here for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Everything okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.16,0:19:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得我刚开始走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Um, I guess I just started walking,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.23,0:20:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果发现不知道去哪儿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}but it turns out I don't really have anywhere to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真服了 你让我好难过 泣就旦土土\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, for God's sake, you're making me sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须得喝一杯了 坐\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Now we have to drink, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好漂亮\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It looks beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,路易斯身体可好\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Louis' health?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.55,0:20:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喝的这是什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What are we drinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.08,0:20:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你最喜欢的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Your favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.23,0:20:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聊聊吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.37,0:20:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前几天 你说\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The other day, you said
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.34,0:20:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有其他的生活方式 其他事可以做\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}there were other ways to live, other things to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.05,0:20:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如说\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不知道任务未经授权\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We didn't know the mission wasn't authorized.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.06,0:21:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 里兹 瓦纳克\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Me, Riz, Vannak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.63,0:21:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一无所知\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We were in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.76,0:21:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说一句\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And for the record,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.47,0:21:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,士官长只是在做他认为正确的事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Chief was just doing what he thought was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.07,0:21:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这正是我担心的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Well, that's what concerns me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很感谢你过来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Look, I appreciate you coming down here
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为你的指挥官辩护\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}to advocate for your CO.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.14,0:21:19.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果士官长越界\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}If the Chief went outside the chain,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.37,0:21:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就需要纪律约束 我明白\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}there needs to be discipline, I get that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.61,0:21:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我们的存在不是跟这儿干坐着\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But we're not built to sit around and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这对我们不好\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's not good for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要进入战斗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We need to be in the fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.28,0:21:32.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会改变决定的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm not gonna change my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.12,0:21:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是让你改\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm not asking you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在正处于战时 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We are at war, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.79,0:21:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们仍然是你最好的武器\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We're still the best weapons you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是建议我在没有队长的情况下\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Are you suggesting I deploy Silver Team
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.66,0:21:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给银队部署任务吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}without its leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.46,0:21:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是  长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.17,0:21:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就我一个\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暂时的 直到约翰没问题\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Temporarily, 'til John's cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.07,0:21:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果有问题呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And if he's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可是士官长啊\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}He's the Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.01,0:21:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20分钟前\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Twenty minutes ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:02.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约翰打晕了负责监视他的士兵\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}John incapacitated the soldiers assigned to monitor him,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.75,0:22:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后逃离此处\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and escaped this facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.62,0:22:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.09,0:22:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他告诉你他的计划了吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Did he share his plans with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,计划 什么啊\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Plans, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.99,0:22:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－什么计划－他在哪儿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- What plans? - Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.66,0:22:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.93,0:22:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次我们谈话\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Last time we spoke,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.13,0:22:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我问过你是否担心约翰的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I asked you if you had concerns
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.83,0:22:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精神稳定性 你说\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}about John's mental stability, and you said---
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－那是之前－什么之前\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- That was before. - Before what?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样多久了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}How long has this been going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.94,0:22:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我不知道－是科塔娜被移除后\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- I don't know. - Since Cortana was removed,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.87,0:22:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是约翰跟星盟特工接触过之后\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}or since John interacted with the Covenant agent?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.01,0:22:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看过档案\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I reviewed the file.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在暗示什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What are you implying?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.82,0:22:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你我都清楚他已经失常了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You and I both know he's not himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.32,0:22:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯 我想跟你说件事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Look, Kai, I, I want to share something with you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.12,0:22:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是以你上司身份告诉你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and this isn't me speaking as your superior, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.06,0:22:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候人是不会好转的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Sometimes people don't get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.17,0:22:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是需要时间\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}He just needs time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.34,0:22:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候 坚持会造成更大的伤害\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Sometimes, we do more damage by holding on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.51,0:23:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能留下来看着他\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I can't stay and watch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.58,0:23:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.75,0:23:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我该怎么做\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell me what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.49,0:23:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候需要几周才能来这里 有时候要几个月\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Sometimes it takes weeks to get here, sometimes months.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.66,0:23:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些人根本就能撑到抵达\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Some never get here at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们离开了牧歌星时是四艘飞船\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We left Madrigal with four ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到的时候只剩一艘了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We arrived with one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.04,0:23:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到那个了吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.87,0:23:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,签订通行证之前 他们会把你安置在那里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That's where they process you before you're indentured.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可不是免费的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's not free.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.88,0:23:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就没有免费的东西\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Nothing is free.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.22,0:23:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.09,0:23:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于你所经历的遭遇\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}For what happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.56,0:23:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别这样\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.26,0:23:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大多数人更惨\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Most people have it worse,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.96,0:23:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候我觉得自己活该\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and sometimes I think I deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.87,0:24:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是对我的惩罚\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm being punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.27,0:24:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－别这么说－这是事实\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Don't talk like that. - It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.87,0:24:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不该在这里的 这不是我的生活\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm not supposed to be here, this isn't my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.78,0:24:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没能履行对我的人民和星球的责任\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I failed my responsibility to my people and my planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.81,0:24:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不能因此责怪自己\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You can't blame yourself for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.88,0:24:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是关哈\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm Kwan Ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.78,0:24:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家族世代\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}My family protected Madrigal
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.39,0:24:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都在保护牧歌星\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}for more generations than anyone can count.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.39,0:24:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等轮到我的时候\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And when it was my turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.63,0:24:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Kwan?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.97,0:24:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该走了 我们可以混进去\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's time to go. We can blend in.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.14,0:24:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得立即行动\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We have to move now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.16,0:25:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脱了 他们会注意到你的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Take it off, they'll notice you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.60,0:25:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－是要躲起来吗－不是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Are we hiding? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.94,0:25:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我们要去哪儿－去找你爸爸回来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Where are we going? - To get your dad back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.67,0:25:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要害怕吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Are we scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.01,0:25:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 跟紧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No. Stay close.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.56,0:25:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把头低下\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Keep your head down.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.46,0:25:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别看\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't look.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.13,0:25:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧往前走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Rising forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.67,0:25:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Keep moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.53,0:26:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－现在要害怕吗－系好安全带\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Are we scared now? - Strap in.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.75,0:26:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一切都会没事的 凯斯\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Everything's gonna be okay, Kes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.75,0:26:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在就去找你爸爸\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We're gonna get your dad now.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.32,0:26:39.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都跟你说了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.46,0:26:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 不  不\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.87,0:26:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我们不会成功的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No, we're not gonna make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.93,0:26:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稳住\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.38,0:26:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.65,0:26:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.38,0:27:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.40,0:27:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.06,0:27:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我行动 然后带凯斯勒离开这里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Wait for my move, then get Kessler out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.97,0:27:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－走舱门－你呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Use the hatch. - What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.94,0:27:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能把你俩送上\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's worth enough to get both of you
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.40,0:27:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－那艘运输船就够了   －不\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- on that transport. - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.61,0:27:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答应我你会把他带上那艘船\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Promise me you'll get him on that ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.31,0:27:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答应我你会保护他\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Promise me you'll protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.84,0:27:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉埃拉\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Laera!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.65,0:27:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－不行 他们会杀了你的－妈妈\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- No, they'll kill you. - Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.18,0:27:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打开 拉埃拉\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Open up, Laera!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.79,0:27:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过会儿见\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'll see you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.66,0:27:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别逼我把这门烧了啊\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't make me torch this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.53,0:27:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她出来了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.70,0:27:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很识相 要不然有可能大家都不好看\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Smart girl, this could have got messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.53,0:27:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－拉埃拉 抱歉 我从没－得了吧 不是针对你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Laera, I'm sorry, I never-- - Give it up, it's not personal.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.87,0:28:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It is!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.98,0:28:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在中继站80米外\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We found Cobalt Team 80 meters
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.35,0:28:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发现了钴队踪迹\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}from the relay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.95,0:28:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们在树上\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They were in the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.79,0:28:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在该区域观察到等离子武器留下的痕迹\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We observed plasma scarring in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.99,0:28:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该是打了他们一个措手不及\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't think they saw it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.63,0:28:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  队长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Thank you, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.23,0:28:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么处理\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}How would you like to handle this?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.13,0:28:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些尸体 长官\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The bodies, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.34,0:28:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有尸体\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There are no bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.20,0:28:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－列为失踪吧－收到\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- I would list it as MIA. - Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.71,0:28:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}走了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.55,0:28:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧 上将\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You all right, Admiral?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.19,0:28:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.66,0:28:54.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我理解\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.56,0:28:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是场悲剧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's a tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.23,0:29:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－你知道吗－你说什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Did you know... - Pardon me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.37,0:29:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把我们的士兵送进敌营的时候\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Did you know that Master Chief's suspicions were valid
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.61,0:29:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道士官长的怀疑是正确的吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}when you sent our soldiers out into a hostile--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.78,0:29:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜欢你的言下之意\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I resent the implication.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.58,0:29:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道你知道什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I want to know what you knew,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.55,0:29:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还想知道你什么时候知道的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and I want to know when you knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.28,0:29:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－冷静一下－冷静\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Just calm down. - Calm down?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.45,0:29:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星盟就在这个星球上\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The Covenant is on this planet!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.35,0:29:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过是时间问题\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It was a matter of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.29,0:29:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一天总要来的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This day was inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.72,0:29:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是个数学问题 上将\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's mathematics, Admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.29,0:29:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次分析 每次模拟\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}In every analysis, every simulation--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.69,0:29:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这他妈不是什么该死的模拟\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This is not a goddamn simulation!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.90,0:29:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 是不是\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Right, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.53,0:29:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我的工作是决定下一步该怎么走\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But it's my job to decide what to do next.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.70,0:29:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须向指挥部发出警报\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We have to alert command.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.44,0:29:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟你保证 你上级已经知道了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I assure you, your superiors are already fully aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.11,0:29:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要启动冬季应急计划\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We need to initiate the Winter Contingency.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.78,0:29:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立即开始疏散平民\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Begin immediate civilian evacuation!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.58,0:29:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结束了 上将 这次我们赢不了的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's over, Admiral. We don't get to win this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.09,0:29:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你发出疏散警报\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}If you send out an evacuation alert,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.13,0:30:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就会陷入混乱 恐慌\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}we'll have chaos, panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.66,0:30:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星盟部队几天前袭击了钴队\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The Covenant element hit Cobalt Team days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.56,0:30:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只能假设星盟舰队就在不远处\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We can only assume the Covenant fleet isn't far behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.00,0:30:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,计划是有的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There is a plan in place,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.77,0:30:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但要做出些艰难的抉择\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}but it's going to require some hard choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.34,0:30:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要知道你是站在我这边的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I need to know that you're with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.98,0:30:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我们不战斗了－我没这么说\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- We're not gonna fight. - I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.45,0:30:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会战斗 只是不会赢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We're going to fight, we're just not going to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.19,0:30:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－这里是致远星－我知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- This is Reach. - I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.03,0:30:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,数百万人的家园\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Home to millions of people--
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.76,0:30:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会尽力挽救\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And we will save what we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.26,0:30:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－这里是我的家－也是我的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- This is my home! - It is my home too!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.27,0:30:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别以为这不会让我付出所有\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't think for a second this doesn't cost me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.37,0:30:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但这是现实 上将\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}but this is reality, Admiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.78,0:30:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要么面对 要么死\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We can either face it or we die.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.78,0:31:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们说话这会儿 重要资产\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Essential assets are being transported
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.19,0:31:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经被运出星球了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}off the planet as we speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.79,0:31:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去收拾东西吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Get your things together.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.16,0:31:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要告诉任何人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.16,0:31:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会逃跑的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I won't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.96,0:31:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我们能赢的那天你再去打仗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You'll fight another day when we can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.87,0:31:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯斯上将 我能指望你吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Admiral Keyes, can I count on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.58,0:31:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去你妈的吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Go fuck yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.09,0:31:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我丈夫呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where's my husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.99,0:31:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－他还活着吗－安塔雷斯\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Is he alive? - Antares?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.06,0:31:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不算迟 安塔雷斯－已经迟了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- It's not too late, Antares. - Yeah, it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.37,0:31:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继续  关\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Go on, Kwan.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.85,0:32:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停下\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Halt.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.68,0:32:01.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.88,0:32:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where's my mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.12,0:32:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一会儿能见到她吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Will I see her soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.56,0:32:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我说实话\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.96,0:32:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.64,0:32:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－城里最棒的 来点不－不了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Best in the city. You want? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.55,0:32:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－试试－不了 谢谢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Try it. - No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.93,0:32:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都有这方面问题\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You've always had this problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.33,0:32:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你掌控不了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You are not in control.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.80,0:32:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说不听指挥\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You mean not controllable.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.57,0:32:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有过协议\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We had an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.73,0:32:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要给我带来的是信息 而不是关注度\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You were to bring me information, not attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.34,0:32:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有消息\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I have information.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.11,0:33:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我想先知道你打算用它做什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But I wanna know what you're gonna do with it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.48,0:33:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们有共同目标 就是赢得战争\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We have a common goal to win the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.11,0:33:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别误把我当朋友对待了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't mistake me for a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.65,0:33:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.26,0:33:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我认为星盟在这里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I believe the Covenant is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.43,0:33:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－在拉面里－在致远星上\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- In the ramen? - On Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.87,0:33:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你认真的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You're serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.27,0:33:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队斯巴达战士失踪了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}A team of Spartans went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.97,0:33:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰队指挥部假装不知道发生了什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}FLEETCOM is pretending they don't know what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.28,0:33:36.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得是星盟\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And do you think it's the Covenant that--
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.64,0:33:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是星盟\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I know it's the Covenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.32,0:33:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我建议你考虑清楚自己说的话\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I suggest you consider what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.55,0:33:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我一直在做的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That's all I've been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.22,0:33:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在想这事 一直在说\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I've been thinking it. I've been saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.12,0:33:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可没人往心里去\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And nobody seems to be listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.22,0:33:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－海军情报局知道的－小声点\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- ONI knows! - Keep your voice down.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.03,0:33:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海军情报局知道的 他们把真相掩盖起来了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}ONI knows. They're covering it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.50,0:33:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们为什么要这么做\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Why would they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.03,0:34:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海军情报局要保护自己\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}The ONI protects itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.57,0:34:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他们树敌\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Make them your enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.00,0:34:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便你是士官长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and it won't matter that you're Master Chief,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.97,0:34:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也都不再有用\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}you will cease to be useful.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.24,0:34:10.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一旦不再有用 那么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And when you cease to be useful, that--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.68,0:34:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－不是 你没明白－你为什么要战斗 约翰\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- No, you're not listening, - Why do you fight, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.05,0:34:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－什么－你战斗 为什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- What? - You fight, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.39,0:34:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了要赢 要保卫我们的家园\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}To win, to defend our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.89,0:34:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要保护人类\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}To preserve humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.76,0:34:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,错 你战斗是因为我让你去战斗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No, you fight because I tell you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.83,0:34:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是个战士 就当好一名战士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You are a soldier, be a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.57,0:34:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是你要做的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This is what you will do.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.74,0:34:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Go back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.94,0:34:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去舰队指挥部\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Go back to FLEETCOM.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.91,0:34:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该拍谁马屁就拍谁马屁\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Kiss whatever ass you have to kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.75,0:34:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去禁闭室服刑\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You go do your time in the brig.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.18,0:34:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,微笑\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.35,0:34:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再也不许提这事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You'll never speak of it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.62,0:34:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们可能会再授予你枚奖章\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They will probably give you another medal.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.13,0:35:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要知道我们都理解对方意思了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I need to know we understand each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.40,0:35:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你什么时候离开海军情报局的 上将\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}When exactly did you leave ONI, Admiral?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.97,0:35:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你从这里走出去 那我就帮不了你了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}If you walk out of here, I won't be able to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.21,0:35:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－你就没离开过－别反抗了 约翰\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- You never left. - Stand down, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.71,0:35:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不这么认为\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.27,0:35:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从来不知道他们其实那么脆弱\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I never understood how fragile they really are.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.34,0:35:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脆弱\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Fragile?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.24,0:35:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 因为你让他们变成那样的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes, because you made them that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.61,0:35:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.08,0:35:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们还是孩子的时候你就把他们带走训练他们\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You took them when they were children.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.58,0:35:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,训练他们\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You conditioned them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.48,0:35:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等他们长大 可以独立思考的时候\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And then when they were old enough to think for themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.45,0:35:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就确保他们永远不会去独立思考\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}you made sure they never would.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.85,0:36:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你把这些植入物放进去\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You put in those pellets.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.42,0:36:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们就再也感受不到欲望\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}So they never had to feel desire
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.46,0:36:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,野心或者偏好\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}or ambition or preference.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.86,0:36:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样他们就不会选择除你之外的人了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}So they would never choose anyone other than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.27,0:36:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 对吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And that's it, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.97,0:36:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 你来干嘛的     －来跟你道别\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Why are you here? - I just came to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.14,0:36:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.11,0:36:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有我 我应该是想让你知道\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And I, I suppose I wanted you to know
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.62,0:36:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的努力没有白费 凯瑟琳\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}that your efforts weren't in vain, Catherine,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.12,0:36:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尽管你看不到那一天\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}you won't be here to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.89,0:36:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你创造出来的东西 虽然可能破碎不堪\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But these things that you made, broken as they may be,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.29,0:36:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但会成为某种\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}they're going to become the foundation
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.03,0:36:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非凡事物的基\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}for something extraordinary.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.13,0:36:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望这最终能给你一些安慰\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And I hope that gives you some comfort in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.67,0:36:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你难道不想知道她是怎么死的吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't you want to know how she died?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.65,0:37:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.62,0:37:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱莉娅 你以为我不知道她是谁吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Julia. Did you think I didn't know who she was?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.36,0:37:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们所有人我都记得\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I remember all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.83,0:37:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是你姐姐\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Especially your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.03,0:37:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她 好奇心很重\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She was... she was so curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.50,0:37:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,问过很多问题\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She used to ask so many questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.37,0:37:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你永远不知道谁能挺过\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But you never know who's going to make it through
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.84,0:37:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,增强手术 谁挺不过来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}the augmentation and who isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.01,0:37:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她没挺过来\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.95,0:37:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.38,0:37:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她快死了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She was dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.89,0:37:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她不清楚原因 理解不了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She didn't know why. She couldn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.69,0:37:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟她说了你刚跟我说的类似的话\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I told her more or less what you just told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.90,0:37:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是即便她看不到\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}That even though she wouldn't see it,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.14,0:38:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也会是接下来前进的一小部分\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}she would be this small part of the next step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.65,0:38:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道她听懂没\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't know if she understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.41,0:38:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她很害怕\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She was so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.28,0:38:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我知道她非常爱你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But I do know that she loved you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.22,0:38:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望这能给你一些安慰\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And I hope that gives you some comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.27,0:38:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.59,0:38:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是要走了么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I thought you were leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.32,0:38:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想留你一个人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I didn't want you to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.93,0:38:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是怪物\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm not a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.98,0:39:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二位重新认识一下吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'll let you two get reacquainted.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.95,0:39:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这样我很难帮你啊\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You are making it very difficult for me to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.99,0:39:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 老大 我们要退出跃迁空间了－听到了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Boss, we're exiting slip space. - I heard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.16,0:39:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我不拦着他们\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I let them have their way...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.19,0:39:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你早就死了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}...you'd already be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.63,0:39:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们对你很好 安塔雷斯\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}We were good to you, Antares.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.96,0:39:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh. Well.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.86,0:39:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你让我勉强度日\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Thank you for allowing me to barely exist
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.07,0:39:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟这帮傻瓜平分一份微薄的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and to scrape out a meager living split four ways
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.00,0:39:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生活费 而你和你丈夫却把牧歌星的钱\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}with these bozos while you and your husband spent
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.14,0:39:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 都花在－你在说什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- all that Madrigal money on-- - What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.07,0:39:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别装傻了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Don't play stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.64,0:39:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你不傻\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I know you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.04,0:39:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一般都可以跟我丈夫讲道理\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I can usually reason with my husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.65,0:39:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但要让他知道这事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}but when he finds out about this--
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.35,0:39:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很担心 我最后一次见到索伦\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm not really worried. Last I see Soren,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.68,0:39:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他正在一艘开往致远星的囚舰上呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}his was on a prison ship headed for Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.52,0:39:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以踏实点吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}So settle in.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.56,0:39:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得有阵子了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It could be a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.56,0:40:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－你个王八蛋     －错 我是机会主义者\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- You're a son of a bitch. - No, I'm an opportunist.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.20,0:40:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东西呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Now, where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.74,0:40:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁去看一下怎么回事\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Would somebody please deal with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.28,0:40:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被吵的都没法想事情了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I can't hear myself think.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.92,0:40:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.69,0:40:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道鲁比·安答应过你什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't know what Ruby Ann promised you,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.96,0:40:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你被耍了 安塔雷斯 现在还不算晚\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}but you are getting played, Antares, and it's not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.56,0:40:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托别说了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Stop, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.80,0:40:39.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,索伦什么都会跟你说\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Soren tells you everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.40,0:40:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他把东西藏哪儿了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You know where he's stashed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.23,0:40:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－藏什么－宝藏\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Stashed what? - The treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.11,0:40:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得很好笑是吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You think this is funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.64,0:40:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我向你保证\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Because I guarantee you...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.92,0:40:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,并不是哦\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}...it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.72,0:41:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你所说的宝藏就是一个装满\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What you call a treasure was a box full
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.59,0:41:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来就不值多少钱的氘币的箱子\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}of deuterium tokens that wasn't worth much to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.76,0:41:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,够了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Heard enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.26,0:41:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁比·安不想要钱\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Ruby Ann doesn't want the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.50,0:41:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她想要碎石星\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She wants The Rubble.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.10,0:41:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冷静\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.90,0:41:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,何必要逼我呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Why are you making me do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.07,0:41:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为我想让凯斯勒当孤儿吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You think I want to leave Kessler an orphan?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.81,0:41:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢那孩子的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I love that kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.51,0:41:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她在嘲笑你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She's laughing at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.62,0:41:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 听到那个声音了吗－听到了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- You hear that sound? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.65,0:41:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你觉得是不是该做点什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah, you think you should do something about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.69,0:41:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在盯着她呀\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.83,0:41:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去看看那是什么声音\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Go see what's making that sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.28,0:41:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－藏哪儿了－她在拖延时间\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Where's the stash? - She's stalling.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.64,0:41:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能闭嘴不\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Would you shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.61,0:42:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不记得有问过任何人意见\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't remember asking anyone's opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.78,0:42:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是舰长\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I'm the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.18,0:42:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的飞船\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This is my ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.95,0:42:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是你最后一次机会 拉埃拉\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and this is your last chance, Laera.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.86,0:42:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,东西在哪儿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.40,0:42:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉不了你 因为根本就不存在\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I can't tell you because it doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.73,0:42:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且就算真存在 我也不会告诉你的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}And if it did exist, I wouldn't tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.37,0:42:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你刚浪费了最后一次机会\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You've just taken it outta my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.51,0:42:33.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记住 我也不想出现接下来发生的事的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Just remember, I didn't want what happens next.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.78,0:43:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有一分钟时间重新考虑你的立场\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You have one minute to rethink your position.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.79,0:43:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没必要走到这步的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It doesn't have to be this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.02,0:43:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想想凯斯勒\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Think of Kessler!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.29,0:43:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,索伦在致远星 谁来照顾他\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}With Soren on Reach, who's gonna look after him?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.53,0:43:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我我想知道的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Just tell me what I wanna kn--
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.91,0:44:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,凯斯勒呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Where's Kessler?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.61,0:44:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Kwan?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.92,0:44:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,关 我在问你问题\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Kwan, I asked you a question--
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.47,0:44:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我把他送上运输船了   －我告诉过你跟他待在一起的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- I put him on the transport. - I told you to stay with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.67,0:44:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－我办不到－为什么不行\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- I couldn't. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.81,0:44:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为那样你就死定了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}'Cause then you'd be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.05,0:44:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟佩雷斯下士谈谈\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I need to speak with Corporal Perez.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.89,0:44:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,－她不在－她在哪儿\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- She's not here. - Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.99,0:45:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是个好姑娘\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She's a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.30,0:45:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的  女士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.77,0:45:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我认为恶魔在跟着你\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}But I think the devil follows you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.05,0:45:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几点了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.88,0:45:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很晚了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}- Late. - Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.66,0:45:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么会在这里\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.76,0:45:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得我们聊过什么吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you remember what we talked about?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.66,0:45:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你让我\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You asked me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.20,0:45:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让他们活捉我\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}To don't let them take me alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.61,0:45:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 是的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.71,0:45:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是今天了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Today's the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.62,0:45:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是今天了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Today's the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.02,0:46:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢天谢地\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Thank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.28,0:46:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呕\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Ohh.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.46,0:46:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人来看你了 爸\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There's someone here to see you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.84,0:46:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱莉娅\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Oh, Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.81,0:47:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朱莉娅\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.47,0:47:29.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佩雷斯下士\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Corporal Perez.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.38,0:48:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从没进过教堂吧\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Never been in a church before, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.65,0:48:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Mnh-mnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.39,0:48:16.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人们来这里寻求安慰\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}People come here for comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.02,0:48:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寻求保护\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}For protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.36,0:48:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寻求答案\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}For answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.77,0:48:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们如愿了吗\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Do they find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.67,0:48:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候可以\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.84,0:48:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呢\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.01,0:48:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在圣所的时候\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}On Sanctuary,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.42,0:48:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,星盟出现之前我\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}before the Covenant came, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.75,0:48:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在雾里 看到些东西\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I saw something... in the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.20,0:48:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说那个女人\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}You mean the woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.70,0:49:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是真实存在的对不对\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}She's real, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.54,0:49:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.87,0:49:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我睡不着\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I don't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.61,0:49:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脑子里一直响着那个声音\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I can't get that sound outta my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.66,0:49:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是在圣所的录音\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}This is a recording from Sanctuary.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.33,0:49:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不止是段干扰\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}It's not just interference.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.80,0:49:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不止是个声音\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Not just a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.80,0:49:38.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面有别的东西\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}There's something underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.68,0:49:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什么\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.65,0:49:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一段祷文\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}A prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.66,0:50:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我给予你们祝福 致远星的人们\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I bring you blessings, people of Reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.13,0:50:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道我来时无有慈悲\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Know that I've come without mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.61,0:50:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无有怜悯\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Without pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.31,0:50:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道我是你们灭亡的工具\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Know that I am the instrument of your extinction.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.55,0:50:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我将此星球献为燔祭\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}I bring this planet forth as a burnt offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.97,0:50:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于这祭坛上 我放上恶魔的头颅\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Upon this altar, I place the head of the Demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.35,0:51:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿他的鲜血引领通往光晕环的道路\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}May his blood mark the way to the Sacred Ring
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.49,0:51:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祝圣我的人民伟大的旅程\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}and consecrate the Great Journey of my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:08.56,0:51:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道我是瓦尔加塔奈\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Know that I am Var 'Gatanai.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.50,0:51:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要知道我是 死神\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Know that I am... Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.38,0:51:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们已经来了\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}They're already here...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.42,0:51:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不对\N{\fs24\1c&HFFDB00&}Aren't they?


